Two publicity films were made with the participation of the voice actors of the Buzz Lightyears: Marcos Mion and Guilherme Briggs.

The movie hero aired during the break of BBB22, also known as the Brazilian Super Bowl.', 'published', '{"order":101,"image":"https://bucket.farra.media/lightyear.png","language":"enUS","slug":"release-lightyear-disney","videos":["https://vimeo.com/703898544","https://vimeo.com/704148968"],"videosHome":["https://vimeo.com/703898544"],"videosHomeOrder":null,"fichaTecnica":[{"title":"Executive Production","content":"Gui Vieira e Tarcila Villa"},{"title":"Direction","content":"Gui Cintra"},{"title":"Production Director","content":"Juliana Hodas"},{"title":"Writing","content":"Andr\u00e9 Brandt, L\u00e9o Parron e Maria Clara Lucci"},{"title":"Production and Creation","content":"Farra"}],"socialMedia":null,"reel":null,"posttype":"jobs","legacy_id":"217423b3-bace-4c3a-81d6-6f654c85f216","legacy_posttype":"jobs","post_thumbnail_id":"637"}', 1719708921000, 1719708921000, 1727799454609);
