Creation, script, production and post production Farra, with the creative exchange and execution indications for the Creators, supporting the brand values without losing the spontaneity of each Creator. The campaign delivered 10 different Reels and over 120 stories of Star+ content.', 'published', '{"order":26,"image":"https://bucket.farra.media/star.avif","language":"enUS","slug":"release-streaming-star","videos":"https://vimeo.com/623638191","videosHome":null,"videosHomeOrder":null,"fichaTecnica":[{"title":"Executive Production","content":"Guilherme Vieira"},{"title":"Producers","content":"Tarcila Villa e Yasmin Persi"},{"title":"Writing","content":"Andr\u00e9 Brandt, Maria Clara, Sergio Barbosa e Gui Cintra"},{"title":"Direction","content":"Gui Cintra"},{"title":"Production","content":"Farra"}],"socialMedia":null,"reel":null,"posttype":"jobs","legacy_id":"32c608db-8fbd-4ec2-b46f-9056faa1bb3b","legacy_posttype":"jobs","post_thumbnail_id":"641"}', 1719707082000, 1719707082000, 1727797519679);
