The developments included episode-specific content, trending topics with guests, promos, subtitled vertical cuts, carousels of quotes and memes, compilations of best moments, as well as extras, behind-the-scenes footage, and pre-premiere materials. A consistent volume of content that helped keep the show present on social media throughout the season.', 'published', '{"videos":["https://vimeo.com/1183770621","https://vimeo.com/1183769773"],"videosHome":null,"videosHomeOrder":null,"order":91,"fichaTecnica":[{"title":"Production:","content":"Farra"},{"title":"Social Media Manager: ","content":"Patrícia Vergili"}],"language":"enUS","socialMedia":null,"reel":null,"posttype":"jobs","slug":"digital-campaign-aberto-ao-publico-temporada-1-e-2-tvglobo","image":"https://bucket.farra.media/aberto ao publico.png","legacy_id":"2538e6d6-6776-455c-bb9f-b98da2de9d57","legacy_posttype":"jobs","post_thumbnail_id":"1218"}', 1776363212000, 1776363212000, 1776364449449);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO edp_posts (id, post_type_id, parent_id, author_id, id_locale_code, title, slug, excerpt, body, status, meta_values, published_at, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (1220, 2, NULL, 'fs9SN8qiF2JCfORn2tkWj3DTiA9qHVhe', 41, 'About Us', 'about-us', 'ENTERTAINMENT FOR ALL MEDIAPartners André Brandt, Gui Cintra and Gui Vieira bring together their experiences in scripts, creation, direction, production, executive production in cinema, television and internet, in the most renowned broadcasters and p', '<h3 data-level="3">ENTERTAINMENT FOR ALL MEDIA</h3><hr><p>Partners André Brandt, Gui Cintra and Gui Vieira bring together their experiences in scripts, creation, direction, production, executive production in cinema, television and internet, in the most renowned broadcasters and platforms in the country, such as TV Globo, Disney+, Netflix, HBO Max, Amazon Prime Video, GNT, Spotify, RecordTV, Deezer, Globoplay, Multishow, TNT, Band, Redetv!, ESPN, Nickelodeon, National Geographic and Warner Channel.</p><p></p>', 'published', '{"order":"","post_thumbnail_id":"1145"}', 1779476628785, 1779476628785, 1779476667093);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO edp_posts (id, post_type_id, parent_id, author_id, id_locale_code, title, slug, excerpt, body, status, meta_values, published_at, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (1222, 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'pilula de farinha.png', 'attachment-jobs-pilula-de-farinha-o-escandalo-que-gerou-vidas-en-us', NULL, NULL, 'published', '{"show_in_menu":false,"menu_options":[],"icon":"line-md:file","mime_type":"image/png","attachment_file":"pilula de farinha.png","attachment_path":"https://bucket.farra.media/pilula de farinha.png","attachment_alt":"PÍLULA DE FARINHA - O ESCÂNDALO QUE GEROU VIDAS"}', NULL, 1776363971808, 1776363971808);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO edp_posts (id, post_type_id, parent_id, author_id, id_locale_code, title, slug, excerpt, body, status, meta_values, published_at, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (1223, 15, NULL, NULL, 39, 'PÍLULA DE FARINHA - O ESCÂNDALO QUE GEROU VIDAS', 'pilula-de-farinha-o-escandalo-que-gerou-vidas-en-us', NULL, 'A co-production of Farra and Warner Bros., this three-episode documentary series recounts the 1998 scandal when tons of placebo of Brazil''s best-selling contraceptive reached pharmacies, resulting in hundreds of unwanted pregnancies. A story that blends drama, police investigation, and the pursuit of justice, created by Jana Medeiros and Heddy Fernandes, with general direction by Cassia Dian and executive production by Verônica Villa and Gui Vieira.', 'published', '{"videos":"https://vimeo.com/1148044414","videosHome":null,"videosHomeOrder":null,"order":107,"fichaTecnica":[],"language":"enUS","socialMedia":null,"reel":null,"posttype":"jobs","legacy_id":"45ad7fe9-2705-4502-aadb-0820964e9d48","legacy_posttype":"jobs","slug":"pilula-de-farinha-o-escandalo-que-gerou-vidas","image":"https://bucket.farra.media/pilula de farinha.png","post_thumbnail_id":"1222"}', 1773848886000, 1773848886000, 1776363971808);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO edp_posts (id, post_type_id, parent_id, author_id, id_locale_code, title, slug, excerpt, body, status, meta_values, published_at, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (1224, 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Featured_Image_Site Farra.png', 'attachment-jobs-aberto-ao-publico-globo-en-us', NULL, NULL, 'published', '{"show_in_menu":false,"menu_options":[],"icon":"line-md:file","mime_type":"image/png","attachment_file":"Featured_Image_Site Farra.png","attachment_path":"https://bucket.farra.media/Featured_Image_Site Farra.png","attachment_alt":"ABERTO AO PÚBLICO | GLOBO"}', NULL, 1773850559934, 1773850559934);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO edp_posts (id, post_type_id, parent_id, author_id, id_locale_code, title, slug, excerpt, body, status, meta_values, published_at, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (1225, 15, NULL, NULL, 39, 'ABERTO AO PÚBLICO | GLOBO', 'aberto-ao-publico-globo-en-us', NULL, 'The audience of anonymous people as the main protagonists of a TV program featuring comedians and celebrities. It was with this purpose that Farra, in co-production with Dromedário, developed, produced, and post-produced two seasons of "Aberto ao Público," a Globo comedy show that mixes comedy with a generous dose of unpretentiousness, irreverence, and embarrassing sincerity, in a completely unpredictable program. In addition to the episodes of this original format, we also produced extra promotional pieces and vertical micro-content that flooded the social media of Globo, the comedians, and Globo guests, showing behind-the-scenes footage, bloopers, and gems that only happen when you put together a stage, an audience, and comedians loose with a microphone.', 'published', '{"videos":["https://vimeo.com/1162256512","https://vimeo.com/1162268067?fl=tl&fe=ec"],"videosHome":null,"videosHomeOrder":null,"order":106,"fichaTecnica":[],"language":"enUS","socialMedia":null,"reel":null,"posttype":"jobs","legacy_id":"1127dd74-c91d-40d0-aba1-d5dc696a139a","legacy_posttype":"jobs","slug":"aberto-ao-publico-globo","image":"https://bucket.farra.media/Featured_Image_Site Farra.png","post_thumbnail_id":"1224"}', 1773850180000, 1773850180000, 1773850559934);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO edp_posts (id, post_type_id, parent_id, author_id, id_locale_code, title, slug, excerpt, body, status, meta_values, published_at, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (1226, 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'lore improta.png', 'attachment-jobs-no-ritmo-da-lore-en-us', NULL, NULL, 'published', '{"show_in_menu":false,"menu_options":[],"icon":"line-md:file","mime_type":"image/png","attachment_file":"lore improta.png","attachment_path":"https://bucket.farra.media/lore improta.png","attachment_alt":"No Ritmo da Lore"}', NULL, 1776364153373, 1776364153373);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO edp_posts (id, post_type_id, parent_id, author_id, id_locale_code, title, slug, excerpt, body, status, meta_values, published_at, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (1227, 15, NULL, NULL, 39, 'No Ritmo da Lore', 'no-ritmo-da-lore-en-us', NULL, 'Produced by FARRA, with script and direction by Andre Brandt, this web series shows the behind-the-scenes of the Viradouro muse, Lore Improta''s, carnival. Over 6 episodes, we''ll follow her outfit selection, filming days, dance classes, rehearsals at the samba school''s headquarters, street rehearsals, and everything else that happens non-stop. Don''t miss it, a new episode every Thursday on YouTube.\r\n', 'published', '{"videos":"https://vimeo.com/1057547400","videosHome":null,"videosHomeOrder":null,"order":104,"fichaTecnica":[{"title":"Direction e Writer:","content":"André Brandt"},{"title":"Production:","content":"Farra"},{"title":"Executive Producer:","content":"Gui Vieira e Tayna Adam"},{"title":"Production Management:","content":"Juliana Hodas"},{"title":"Executive Production Assistance:","content":" Beatriz Fontana Carvalho"},{"title":"Financer:","content":" Andressa Carrijo"},{"title":"Design:","content":"Beatriz Vidal"},{"title":"","content":""},{"title":"Motion Design:","content":"Serginho Dimi"},{"title":"Cinematography: ","content":"Alex Tavares"},{"title":"Filmmaker Rio de Janeiro: ","content":"Miguel Souza"},{"title":"Filmmaker Salvador: ","content":"Tarcisio Sampaio"},{"title":"Edition: ","content":"Mike Lopes Prado"},{"title":"Post-production coordination: ","content":"Frederico Kesselring"},{"title":"Filmmaker São Paulo: ","content":"Victor Lima"},{"title":"Audio Production: ","content":"DreamBox"},{"title":"Color: ","content":"Gabriel Ranzani"}],"language":"enUS","socialMedia":null,"reel":null,"posttype":"jobs","legacy_id":"be1aa998-8848-420c-ab2d-3ba5fdf70ea1","legacy_posttype":"jobs","slug":"no-ritmo-da-lore","image":"https://bucket.farra.media/lore improta.png","post_thumbnail_id":"1226"}', 1739790091000, 1739790091000, 1776364153373);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO edp_posts (id, post_type_id, parent_id, author_id, id_locale_code, title, slug, excerpt, body, status, meta_values, published_at, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (1228, 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'RAFI.png', 'attachment-jobs-rafi-en-us', NULL, NULL, 'published', '{"show_in_menu":false,"menu_options":[],"icon":"line-md:file","mime_type":"image/png","attachment_file":"RAFI.png","attachment_path":"https://bucket.farra.media/RAFI.png","attachment_alt":"RAFI"}', NULL, 1776169449853, 1776169449853);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO edp_posts (id, post_type_id, parent_id, author_id, id_locale_code, title, slug, excerpt, body, status, meta_values, published_at, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (1229, 15, NULL, NULL, 39, 'RAFI', 'rafi-en-us', NULL, 'After six years carving out his place in one of the most competitive stand-up comedy scenes in the world, Rafinha Bastos is preparing to record his first English-language special. This exclusive documentary offers a unique behind-the-scenes look at the three days leading up to the recording, following the comedian through his routine at comedy clubs across the US, while he reflects on his journey—from Brazil to the long-awaited international recognition.', 'published', '{"videos":"https://vimeo.com/1047243492","videosHome":null,"videosHomeOrder":null,"order":99,"fichaTecnica":[{"title":"Production:","content":"Farra"},{"title":"General Direction and Screenplay","content":"André Brandt"},{"title":"Digital Art: ","content":"Beatriz Vidal"},{"title":"Producers:","content":" Gui Vieira, Gui Cintra, André Brandt"},{"title":"Cinematography:","content":"Alex Tavares"},{"title":"Executive Producer:","content":"Gui Vieira e Tayna Adam"},{"title":"Assistente Producer:","content":"Beatriz Fontada"},{"title":"Producer:","content":"Juliana Hodas"},{"title":"Post-production Coordination: ","content":"Fred Kesselring"},{"title":"Edition:","content":"Dreiky F."},{"title":"Financer:","content":"Andressa Carrijo"},{"title":"Edition Assistent:","content":"Mike Prado"},{"title":"Color:","content":"Gabriel Ranzani"},{"title":"Sound Producer:","content":" Dream Box Produções LTDA "},{"title":"Sound Editing and Mixing:","content":"Guilherme Picolo e Tullio Zarpao"},{"title":"Completion: ","content":"Fred Kesselring e Dreiky F."},{"title":"Subtitles: ","content":"Dreiky Fraga"},{"title":"Executive Producer of Post-Sound","content":"Daniel Picolo "}],"language":"enUS","socialMedia":null,"reel":null,"posttype":"jobs","legacy_id":"9494ce47-96a4-4cc4-9a64-d004acb0b177","legacy_posttype":"jobs","slug":"rafi","image":"https://bucket.farra.media/RAFI.png","post_thumbnail_id":"1228"}', 1773863323000, 1773863323000, 1776169449853);
